Name: Kenneth Thornhill
Date: September 4th, 2013
Card Name: Lightning Bolt
Card type: Offensive
Pick-up ability: Strike any player within 5 spaces in any direction with lightning, making them discard 3 cards.
Equip Ability: Strike any player within 5 spaces in any direction with lightning, making them discard 3 cards. Can also be used on the player landed on.
